    <h1 class="homeh1">Welcome to Whistler Public Library</h1>
    <table border="0" align="center" style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td align="center" valign="middle"><br />
<table border="0" cellspacing="4" cellpadding="4"
style="width: 290px; height: 103px; float: left;">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="background-color: #cc6600;">
<p><span class="whitetext">&nbsp;LIBRARY HOURS<br />
</span></p>
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td style="background-color: #e1ecf1;">Monday to Thursday</td>
<td style="background-color: #e1ecf1;">10 am to 7 pm</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td style="background-color: #e1ecf1;">Friday</td>
<td style="background-color: #e1ecf1;">10 am to 6 pm</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td style="background-color: #e1ecf1;">Saturday &amp; Sunday</td>
<td style="background-color: #e1ecf1;">11 am to 5 pm</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</td>
<td valign="top" style="text-align: center;"><a
href="http://www.youtube.com/embed/rnfq6BvPG6E"><img src="/media/108792/home-video.jpg" width="375" height="180" alt="Watch the Whistler Library video" style="margin: 4px 0 0 10px;"/></a></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>

<p><strong>Located in Whistler, British Columbia</strong> in the
coastal mountains of western Canada, Whistler Public Library is one
of the busiest libraries in the province. The library opened the
doors of its spectacular permanent home on January 26, 2008 and
serves as a community hub for locals, seasonals, and visitors.
Welcome to Whistler's Living Room!</p>

<p style="margin-bottom: 25px;"><strong>What is your public library
worth to you?&nbsp;</strong> Use our handy new <a
href="/location-and-hours/library-value-calculator/" title="Library Value Calculator">Library
Value Calculator</a> to&nbsp;calculate how much you would pay out
of pocket for&nbsp;the library services that you use.&nbsp; Your
library&nbsp;really&nbsp;is the "best deal in town".</p>

<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="features"
style="width: 100%;">
