<h2>Your Library - Your Gateway to Knowledge&nbsp;</h2>

<ul>
<li>Under <a href="/find-books-and-more/"
title="Search the Catalogue">Find Books &amp; More</a> you will
find our Library Catalogue, book recommendations,&nbsp;digital
audiobooks that you can download at home,&nbsp;a form to suggest a
purchase, and links to other libraries.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li><a href="/location-and-hours/"
title="Location and Hours">Using&nbsp;the Library</a> section
offers information on getting a library card, borrrowing and
renewing library materials, information on computer access in the
library,&nbsp;booking the Community Room for meetings in the
library&nbsp;and more.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>Our <a href="/research-and-homework/"
title="Research and Homework">Research &amp; Homework</a> section
provides online resources on a variety of topics.&nbsp;</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>Stay up-to-date with the <a href="/events-and-programs/"
title="Events and Programs">Events Calendar</a>, <a
href="/teens/" title="Teens">Teens</a> and <a
href="/kids/" title="Kids">Kids</a> sections. Both the
Teens and Kids areas include a blog where you can add
comments.</li>
</ul>
